"Coloca un elemento (imagen, texto, etc.) atrás o adelante de otro con los "
"iconos :guilabel:`Enviar atrás` o :guilabel:`Traer al frente`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Change block position"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla del cambio de posición de un bloque"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:181
msgid ""
"To resize a block, click and drag the dots around its edges to adjust it as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Para cambiar el tamaño de un bloque, haz clic y arrastra los puntos "
"alrededor de sus bordes para ajustarlo según sea necesario."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Adapt block size"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla del cambio de tamaño de un bloque"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:187
msgid ":doc:`General theme <themes>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Tema general <themes>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:190
msgid "Layout: grid and columns"
msgstr "Diseño: tablas y columnas"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:192
msgid ""
"For most building blocks, you can choose between two layout "
"styles: :ref:`grid <website/building_blocks/grid>` or :ref:`columns (cols) "
"<website/building_blocks/cols>`. To change the default layout style, click "
"the block, go to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, and set "
"the :guilabel:`Layout` field to :guilabel:`Grid` or :guilabel:`Cols`."
msgstr ""
"En la mayoría de los bloques de creación puedes elegir entre dos estilos de "
"diseño: :ref:`cuadrícula <website/building_blocks/grid>` o :ref:`columnas "
"(cols) <website/building_blocks/cols>`. Haz clic en un bloque para cambiar "
"su estilo de diseño predeterminado, ve a la pestaña :guilabel:`Personalizar` "
"y selecciona :guilabel:`Cuadrícula` o :guilabel:`Columnas` en el campo "
":guilabel:`Diseño`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:200
msgid "Grid"
msgstr "Cuadrícula"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:202
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Grid` layout allows you to reposition and resize elements, "
"such as images or text, by dragging and dropping them. When :guilabel:`Grid` "
"is selected, additional options are available to :guilabel:`Add Elements` by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Image`, :guilabel:`Text`, or :guilabel:`Button`."
msgstr ""
"El diseño de :guilabel:`cuadrícula` te permite reposicionar y cambiar el "
"tamaño de los elementos, como imágenes o texto, al arrastrarlos y soltarlos. "
"Al seleccionar :guilabel:`Cuadrícula` aparecen otras opciones para "
":guilabel:`agregar elementos` si haces clic en :guilabel:`Imagen`, "
":guilabel:`Texto` o :guilabel:`Botón`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:-1
msgid ""
"When the grid layout is selected, choose an image and drag and drop it where "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Cuando se selecciona el diseño de tabla puede elegir una imagen y "
"arrastrarla y soltarla a donde la necesite."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:212
msgid "Cols"
msgstr "Columnas"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:214
msgid ""
"Choosing the :guilabel:`Cols` layout allows you to determine the number of "
"elements per line within the block. To do so, select the block to modify, "
"click the dropdown next to the :guilabel:`Cols` field, and adjust the "
"number. You can then modify a specific column's settings using the options "
"in the :guilabel:`Column` section of the :guilabel:`Customize` tab."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionar el diseño de :guilabel:`columnas` te permite determinar el "
"número de elementos por línea dentro del bloque. Para ello, selecciona el "
"bloque a modificar, haz clic en la lista desplegable junto al campo "
":guilabel:`Columnas` y cambia el número. Después podrás modificar los "
"ajustes de una columna en específico con las opciones de la sección "
":guilabel:`Columna` de la pestaña :guilabel:`Personalizar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:220
msgid ""
"By default, :doc:`on mobile devices <visibility>`, only one element (column) "
"is visible per line to ensure that content remains easily readable and "
"accessible on smaller screens. To adjust the value, click the :icon:`fa-"
"mobile` (:guilabel:`mobile icon`) at the top of the website editor and adapt "
"the number of columns. Shapes are hidden by default on mobiles."
msgstr ""
"De forma predeterminada, :doc:`en los dispositivos móviles <visibility>` "
"solo hay un elemento (columna) visible por línea para garantizar que el "
"contenido siga siendo legible y accesible con facilidad en pantallas más "
"pequeñas. Para ajustar el valor, haz clic en el icono :icon:`fa-mobile` "
"(:guilabel:`celular`) que se encuentra en la parte superior del editor del "
"sitio web y modifica el número de columnas. Las formas están ocultas de "
"forma predeterminada para los celulares."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:228
msgid "Duplicate a building block"
msgstr "Duplicar un bloque de creación"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:230
msgid ""
"To duplicate a building block, click the :icon:`fa-clone` "
"(:guilabel:`duplicate`) icon at the top of the :guilabel:`Customize` tab. "
"Once duplicated, the new block appears on the page beneath the original one."
msgstr ""
"Para duplicar un bloque de creación, haz clic en el icono :icon:`fa-clone` "
"(:guilabel:`duplicar`) que se encuentra en la parte superior de la pestaña "
":guilabel:`Personalizar`. Una vez que lo hayas duplicado aparecerá en la "
"página abajo del bloque original."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:237
msgid "Save a custom building block"
msgstr "Guardar un bloque de creación personalizado"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:239
msgid ""
"You can save a customized building block to reuse it elsewhere. To do so, "
"select it, navigate to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-floppy-o` (:guilabel:`floppy disk`) icon. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Save and reload` button in the popup to confirm saving your "
"custom block."
msgstr ""
"Puedes guardar un bloque de creación personalizado para volver a utilizarlo "
"en otro lado. Para ello, selecciónalo, ve a la pestaña "
":guilabel:`Personalizar` y haz clic en el :icon:`fa-floppy-o` "
"(:guilabel:`disquete`). Haz clic en el botón :guilabel:`Guardar y actualizar`"
" de la ventana emergente para confirmar que quieres guardar el bloque."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:243
msgid ""
"To add a saved building block to the page, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Blocks` tab and drag and drop the :guilabel:`Custom` block "
"from the :guilabel:`Categories` section. In the popup that opens, click the "
"desired block in the :guilabel:`Custom` category."
msgstr ""
"Para agregar un bloque de creación que hayas guardado a la página, ve a la "
"pestaña :guilabel:`Bloques` y arrastra y suelta el bloque "
":guilabel:`personalizado` de la sección :guilabel:`Categorías`. Esta acción "
"abrirá una ventana emergente, allí haz clic en el bloque que quieres en la "
"categoría :guilabel:`Personalizado`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:248
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Insert a block` popup, click :icon:`fa-pencil` "
"(:guilabel:`edit`) to rename the custom block or :icon:`fa-trash` "
"(:guilabel:`delete`) to delete it."
msgstr ""
"En la ventana emergente :guilabel:`Inserta un bloque`, haz clic en :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` (:guilabel:`editar`) para cambiar el nombre del bloque personalizado "
"o en :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`papelera`) para eliminarlo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:254
msgid "Create an anchor link"
msgstr "Crear un enlace ancla"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:256
msgid ""
"Anchor links are hyperlinks that direct users to a **specific section** of a "
"page. To create an anchor link for a block, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Los enlaces ancla son hipervínculos que dirigen a los usuarios a una **"
"sección específica** de una página. Sigue estos pasos para crear uno:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:259
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the block you want to link to."
msgstr ""
"Haz clic en :guilabel:`Editar` y selecciona el bloque que quieres vincular."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:260
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`link`) at the top of "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab."
msgstr ""
"Haz clic en el icono :icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`enlace`) que se encuentra "
"en la parte superior de la pestaña :guilabel:`Personalizar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:261
msgid ""
"To edit the default anchor name, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the green popup "
"message that opens."
msgstr ""
"Para editar el nombre de ancla predeterminado, haz clic en :guilabel:`Editar`"
" en el mensaje emergente verde que aparecerá."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:262
msgid "Replace the anchor name and click :guilabel:`Save & copy`."
msgstr ""
"Reemplaza el nombre de ancla y haz clic en :guilabel:`Guardar y copiar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:264
msgid ""
"Once the anchor is saved, you can :ref:`link to it <website/elements/links>` "
"from anywhere on your website."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que hayas guardado el ancla podrás :ref:`enlazarlo <website/elements/"
"links>` desde cualquier parte de tu sitio web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:3
msgid "Elements"
msgstr "Elementos"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:5
msgid ""
"Elements help structure and present content effectively. They range from "
"text-based components like :ref:`titles <website/elements/"
"titles>`, :ref:`lists <website/elements/lists>` and :ref:`text highlights "
"<website/elements/text_highlights>` to interactive ones such "
"as :ref:`buttons <website/elements/buttons>` and :ref:`links <website/"
"elements/links>`. Visual elements like :ref:`images <website/elements/"
"images>`, :ref:`icons <website/elements/icons>`, :ref:`videos <website/"
"elements/videos>`, and :ref:`animations <website/elements/animations>` can "
"also be added to improve content presentation and organization."
msgstr ""
"Los elementos ayudan a estructurar y presentar el contenido de forma eficaz. "
"Estos pueden ser componentes basados en texto, como :ref:`títulos <website/"
"elements/titles>`, :ref:`listas <website/elements/lists>` y :ref:`resaltados "
"de texto <website/elements/text_highlights>` o elementos interactivos, como "
":ref:`botones <website/elements/buttons>` y :ref:`enlaces <website/elements/"
"links>`. También puede agregar elementos visuales como :ref:`imágenes <"
"website/elements/images>`, :ref:`iconos <website/elements/icons>`, :ref:`"
"videos <website/elements/videos>` y :ref:`animaciones <website/elements/"
"animations>` para mejorar la presentación y organización del contenido."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:13
msgid "To add or modify a website element:"
msgstr "Para agregar o modificar un elemento del sitio web:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:15
msgid "Navigate to the relevant website page and click on :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Vaya ala página correspondiente del sitio web y haga clic en "
":guilabel:`Editar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:16
msgid ""
"Click the section on the page where you want to add or modify an element."
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en la sección de la página donde desea agregar o modificar un "
"elemento."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:17
msgid "Make the necessary changes."
msgstr "Haga los cambios necesarios."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:18
msgid "Click on :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Haga clic en :guilabel:`Guardar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:21
msgid ""
"The default styles for headings, buttons, links, and paragraph text, for "
"example, are defined in the :doc:`Theme tab <themes>` of the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Los estilos predeterminados de los encabezados, botones, enlaces y párrafos "
"se definen en la :doc:`pestaña Tema <themes>` del editor del sitio web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:-1
msgid "Type / to add website elements."
msgstr "Escribir / para agregar elementos al sitio web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:30
msgid "Titles"
msgstr "Títulos"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:32
msgid ""
"Titles define headings and organize website content into different levels "
"for clarity and structure. To insert a title, type `/title`, choose the "
"heading style (:guilabel:`Heading 1`, :guilabel:`Heading 2`, "
"or :guilabel:`Heading 3`), and type the text."
msgstr ""
"Los títulos definen los encabezados y organizan el contenido del sitio web "
"en diferentes niveles para que haya mayor claridad y estructura. Escriba "
"`título` para insertar uno, elija el estilo correspondiente (:guilabel:`"
"Título 1`, :guilabel:`Título 2` o :guilabel:`Título 3`) y escriba el texto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:37
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type the text, select it, and choose the appropriate style "
"from the :guilabel:`Inline Text` section in the :guilabel:`Customize` tab of "
"the website editor. Additional formatting options, such as fonts and colors, "
"are also available in this section."
msgstr ""
"También puede escribir el texto, seleccionarlo y elegir el estilo adecuado "
"en la sección :guilabel:`Texto` en línea en la pestaña "
":guilabel:`Personalizar` del editor del sitio web. Esta sección también "
"cuenta con otras opciones de formato, como fuentes y colores."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:44
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Botones"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:46
msgid ""
"Buttons are interactive elements that allow to link to another page or to a "
"page anchor. To insert a button:"
msgstr ""
"Los botones son elementos interactivos que permiten vincular otras páginas o "
"anclas de páginas. Para insertar un botón:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:49
msgid "Type `/button`."
msgstr "Escriba `/botón`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:50
msgid "Enter the button's label in the :guilabel:`Link Label` field."
msgstr ""
"Escriba la etiqueta del botón en el campo :guilabel:`Etiqueta del enlace`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:51
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`URL or Email`. Type `/` to search for a page and `#` to "
"link to an anchor."
msgstr ""
"Agregue la :guilabel:`URL o correo electrónico`. Escriba `/` para buscar una "
"página o `#` para vincular un ancla."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:52
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Style`, :guilabel:`Size`, and :guilabel:`Layout` to "
"define the button's appearance."
msgstr ""
"Configure el :guilabel:`estilo`, :guilabel:`tamaño` y :guilabel:`diseño` "
"para definir la apariencia del botón."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:54
msgid ""
"If needed, toggle the switch to open the linked page or anchor in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Si es necesario, presione el botón correspondiente para abrir la página "
"vinculada o ancla en una nueva pestaña."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:55
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Apply` to save changes."
msgstr "Haga clic en :guilabel:`Aplicar` para guardar los cambios."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:58
msgid ""
"To modify an existing button, click the button and edit the options in "
"the :guilabel:`Inline text` section of the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Para modificar un botón existente, haga clic en el botón y edite las "
"opciones en la sección :guilabel:`Texto en línea` del editor del sitio web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:66
msgid "To insert an image:"
msgstr "Para insertar una imagen:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:68
msgid "Type `/image`."
msgstr "Escriba `/imagen`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:69
msgid ""
":doc:`Search the Unsplash database </applications/general/integrations/"
"unsplash>` or click :guilabel:`Upload an image` to choose a file from your "
"local images."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Busque una imagen en la base de datos de Unsplash </applications/"
"general/integrations/unsplash>` o haga clic en :guilabel:`Subir una imagen` "
"para elegir una de sus archivos locales."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:71
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr "Haga clic en :guilabel:`Agregar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:72
msgid ""
"To customize the image, click on the image and edit the options in "
"the :guilabel:`Image` section of the website editor. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Para personalizar la imagen, haga clic en ella y edite las opciones en la "
"sección :guilabel:`Imagen` del editor del sitio web. Por ejemplo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:75
msgid ":guilabel:`Replace` the image."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reemplace` la imagen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:76
msgid ""
"Define an `alt tag <https://help.siteimprove.com/support/solutions/articles/"
"80000448480-where-are-alt-tags- used-and-why-are-they-important>`_ in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` field."
msgstr ""
"Defina una `etiqueta alternativa <https://help.siteimprove.com/support/"
"solutions/articles/80000448480-where-are-alt-tags-used-and-why-are-they-"
"important>`_ en el campo :guilabel:`Descripción`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:78
msgid ""
"Enter a title tag in the :guilabel:`Tooltip` field. This text will appear "
"when visitors hover their mouse over the image."
msgstr ""
"Escriba una etiqueta de título en el campo :guilabel:`Información sobre "
"herramientas`. Este texto aparecerá cuando los visitantes pasen el cursor "
"sobre la imagen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:80
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Shape`; some shapes also allow for color customization."
msgstr ""
"Agregue una :guilabel:`forma`. Puede cambiar el color de algunas de ellas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:81
msgid ""
"Adjust the image's :guilabel:`Width`, e.g., to improve performance. A "
"smaller size may be suggested if it is sufficient for display."
msgstr ""
"Ajuste el :guilabel:`ancho` de la imagen. Esto podría ayudarle a mejorar el "
"rendimiento y puede aparecer una sugerencia para que reduzca su tamaño si "
"este es suficiente para la visualización."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:83
msgid "Resize the image using the :guilabel:`Transform` tool."
msgstr ""
"Use la herramienta :guilabel:`Transformar` para cambiar el tamaño de la "
"imagen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:84
msgid ""
"Adjust the :guilabel:`Padding` to add space (in pixels) around the image."
msgstr ""
"Ajuste el :guilabel:`padding` para agregar espacio (en píxeles) alrededor de "
"la imagen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:85
msgid "Etc."
msgstr "Entre otras cosas."

